@014=~CAVALIER: This class represents the most common picture of the knight: the chivalrous warrior who epitomizes honor, courage, and loyalty. The cavalier is specialized in battling "classical" evil monsters such as demons and dragons.

Advantages:
– +3 bonus to hit and damage rolls against all fiendish and draconic creatures.
– May cast Remove Fear once per day per level.
– Immune to charm, fear, poison, and morale failure.
– 20% resistance to fire and acid.

Disadvantages:
– May not use Aura of Faith ability.
– May not use missile weapons.~
