When a monk reaches 11th level, her flurry of blows ability improves. In addition to the standard single extra attack <PRO_HESHE> gets from flurry of blows, <PRO_HESHE> gets another one without any penalties.
When using flurry of blows, a monk may attack only with unarmed strikes, with dagger(s) or quarterstaff.

